message: لما بدور على الوظايف المتاحة فى مجال ال IT فى مصر بلاقي بعد asp.net و php developers بلاقي ساعات java developers.. كنت عايز اعرف اغلبية شغل الجافا فى مصر بيبقي ويب برضو ولا حاجة تاني ؟

data.message: Company I used to intern at used Java to develop programs for internal data analysis, transactions, keeping record of contracts, suggesting contract templates, etc etc. I'd imagine other companies of the same scale do the same.

Most of development in any language in any place is web :D
I would also comfortably tell you that Java web developers are the best paid developers in Egypt (It we are talking about traditional full-time jobs).
لو جافا ممكن تشتغل موبايل كمان(اندرويد)، مش ويب بس.
